According to the changlelog :
https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/r1.5/RELEASE.md#major-features-and-improvements

Conv2D, Conv2DBackpropInput, Conv2DBackpropFilter now supports arbitrary dilations with GPU and cuDNNv6 support.

body:
According to the changlelog : 
https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/r1.5/RELEASE.md#major-features-and-improvements

Conv2D, Conv2DBackpropInput, Conv2DBackpropFilter now supports arbitrary dilations with GPU and cuDNNv6 support.
